title: Fishing Active / AFK (Barbarian)
comment_one: You want to max "Idle Skilling" and "Brute Efficiency", then  "Fist of Rage"
comment_two:
Maxing "Absolute Unit" and "Firmly Grasp it" gives some efficiency.
"Tempestous Emotions" provide extra xp.
comment_three:
Max "Worming Undercover" and "Catching some ZZZ's", boost "All fish diet" if you're going for xp
*1 = Boost it to around your minigame score.
*2 = Excess points here.
notes: Due to prowess effect not working active, AFK fishing will always be better if you have at least 2x prowess
